<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<chapter xml:id="ch-four-chord-grids" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Four-Chord-Grids</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>The Chord Shapes shown can be moved to different positions on the keyboard and take the name of the Root Chord. Thus, if you know the shape of one chord type, you know the shape of all chords of that type in that shape or inversion.</p>
  </introduction>

  <section xml:id="sec-four-chord-grids-main">
    <title>Four Grids</title>

    <!-- Row 1: Fig 1 and Fig 2 -->
    <figure xml:id="fig-chord-grids-row1">
      <caption></caption>
      <sidebyside widths="47% 47%" margins="3%">

      <!-- Fig 1 -->
      <stack>
        <image xml:id="img-grid-c-major">
          <latex-image>
\begin{tikzpicture}[scale=0.66, transform shape]
\pgfmathsetmacro{\isoangle}{60}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\vv}{8}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\hh}{6}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\vlen}{1.5}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\ang}{\isoangle/2}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\dlen}{(\vlen/2) / sin(\ang)}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\hlen}{(\vlen/2) / tan(\ang)}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\xmax}{\hh*\hlen}
\pgfmathsetmacro{\ymax}{\vv*\vlen}
\drawgridandnotes
% ---- angled row 1: C  C#/Db  D  Eb/D#  E ----
\gn{5}{1.5}{C}{1}
\gn{4}{2}{C$\sharp$, D$\flat$}{0}
\gn{3}{2.5}{D}{0}
\gn{2}{3}{E$\flat$, D$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{1}{3.5}{E}{0}
% ---- angled row 2: Eb/D#  E  F  F#/Gb  G ----
\gn{5}{2.5}{E$\flat$, D$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{4}{3}{E}{1}
\gn{3}{3.5}{F}{0}
\gn{2}{4}{G$\flat$, F$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{1}{4.5}{G}{0}
% ---- angled row 3: F#/Gb  G  Ab/G#  A  Bb/A# ----
\gn{5}{3.5}{G$\flat$, F$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{4}{4}{G}{1}
\gn{3}{4.5}{A$\flat$, G$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{2}{5}{A}{0}
\gn{1}{5.5}{B$\flat$, A$\sharp$}{0}
% ---- angled row 4: A  Bb/A#  B  C  C#/Db ----
\gn{5}{4.5}{A}{0}
\gn{4}{5}{B$\flat$, A$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{3}{5.5}{B}{1}
\gn{2}{6}{C}{0}
\gn{1}{6.5}{C$\sharp$, D$\flat$}{0}
% ---- angled row 5: C  C#/Db  D  Eb/D#  E ----
\gn{5}{5.5}{C}{0}
\gn{4}{6}{C$\sharp$, D$\flat$}{0}
\gn{3}{6.5}{D}{0}
\gn{2}{7}{E$\flat$, D$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{1}{7.5}{E}{0}
% ---- angled row 6: Eb/D#  E  F  F#/Gb  G ----
\gn{5}{6.5}{E$\flat$, D$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{4}{7}{E}{0}
\gn{3}{7.5}{F}{0}
\gn{2}{8}{G$\flat$, F$\sharp$}{0}
\gn{1}{8.5}{G}{0}
\end{tikzpicture}
          </latex-image>
        </image>
        <image xml:id="img-notation-grid1" source="notation/staff-grid1" width="150%">
          <shortdescription>Notation for Fig 1 on treble staff</shortdescription>
        </image>
        <p><em>Cmaj7</em>
          </p>
      </stack>

